{"tid":1891760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞清楚，香港不存在「政府派錢」，只有「政府還錢」","createTime":"2020-02-22T05:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T05:50:43.000Z","uid":255105,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"677bd4ff76d79495ae2df013313fc38df8b5ee87","tid":1891760,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:30:59.000Z","msg":"派咩撚野錢？啲錢本身係我地既，我地只係攞返應得既野。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地係債主！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個極權殖民政府並非民主產生，佢地既一切都係依靠掠奪得黎。錢係佢地手上只係不義之財，權係不義之權，武力係不義之武。<br />\n<br />\n我地要攞返應得既一切，錢、權、武力，同埋未來。佢地唔還，就打到佢還。呢個先係正確既mindset。"},{"pid":"3b564d9a9655e313faf076323799d0ea02fbfd74","tid":1891760,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"咁叻咪唔交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5823c8be3bdce5c32794408c7454bd9637b5e422","tid":1891760,"uid":60977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n有無辨法說班公司唔交稅<br />\n最好斷曬所有稅"},{"pid":"c01520ab82a6621efd177b2d1f98db3ebd5709e8","tid":1891760,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b564d9a9655e313faf076323799d0ea02fbfd74","tid":1891760,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"咁叻咪唔交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:39:40.000Z","msg":"罷緊唔通又話你知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436712febb13c6ecaa0b3b98188407b9601320b5","tid":1891760,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"政府瘋狂派錢俾支那狗喎, 樓主瞓咗幾耐?"},{"pid":"f3ebcfdcd75e5602705895e3941f8573f868bcd5","tid":1891760,"uid":255105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"436712febb13c6ecaa0b3b98188407b9601320b5","tid":1891760,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-